ìíŸ@6645801bbcf21f9491c751cddbbd3f99d3f447672ca062196db2808570f9698e⁄	vTitle: This week in Nushell #253
Path: Nushell
Content:
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13259] added context to the I/O error messages in 
``nu_cmd_plugin::util::modify_plugin_file()``
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13218] mitigated the poor interaction between ndots expansion and non-path strings
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13265] updated the Nu version to v0.95 and setup-nu for workflows
t-mart 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13258] addressed surprising symlink resolution for std 
``path add``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13217] implemented autoloading
weirdan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13256] added support for multiple attributes to 
``query web -a``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13241] added 
``char nul``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13212] fixed usage parsing for commands defined in CRLF (windows) files
suimong 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13246] fixed a find command output bug with ByteStream input
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13238] upgraded Polars to 0.41
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13233] updated lock via cargo check to fix CI
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13231] bumped the version to 0.95.1
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13224] converted the perf function to a macro, then used the perf macro within the polars plugin
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13221] bumped to 0.95.0
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13222] updated and added ls examples
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13220] used 
``IntoValue``
 and 
``FromValue``
 derive macros in 
``nu_plugin_example``
 for example usage
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13213] defined keywords
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13115] added typed path forms
ito-hiroki 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13209] made the subcommands (
``from {csv, tsv, ssv}``
) 0-based for consistency
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13170] enabled reloading changes to a submodule
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13131] restricted strings beginning with a quote to also end with a quote
